MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2007-0076. IBM Corp. v. Franklin Cty. Bd. of Revision.

Franklin App. No. 06AP-108, 2006-Ohio-5258. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Franklin County. Upon consideration of the joint motion to remand to the Franklin County Board of Revision,

It is ordered by the court that the motion is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
